data.description: A 3-bedroom, 2-bath home with many updates located on a quiet street. The spacious living area with a wood-burning fireplace and a fully fenced backyard adds to the comfort and privacy. The property's proximity to the freeway, downtown, dining, and shopping makes it convenient for residents. Additionally, the presence of a concrete pad for outdoor activities is a nice feature, offering space for various outdoor pursuits.
